Incarnate_Punch.help: The Olympian Guard wields a large portion of the power of Tyrant. These super soldier clones are capable of crushing their foes in close quarters with energy melee attacks.
Incarnate_Punch.targetHelp: The Incarnate power flowing through the Olympian Guard has reduced your defense and your resistance to smashing damage.

Dull_Pain.help: The Olympian Guard is able to shrug off wounds that would kill a normal person. Dull Pain not only increases their maximum hit points, but it will also heal them for a large portion of their health.
Dull_Pain.targetHelp: The Olympian Guard is able to shrug off wounds that would kill a normal person. Dull Pain not only increases their maximum hit points, but it will also heal them for a large portion of their health.

Unstoppable.help: When you activate this power, you not only become extremely resistant to most damage, but also to Disorient, Immobilization, Hold, and Sleep effects. Endurance recovery is also increased. Unstoppable costs little Endurance to activate, but when it wears off you are left exhausted, and drained of half of your Endurance. Recharge: Very Long
Unstoppable.shortHelp: Self, +Res(Disorient, Sleep, Hold, Immobilize, All DMG but Psionics)
